  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At 17th level you have so much knowledge and contacts to get to any place or step in society. By using your own @Compendium[world.profession-features.KX3mk6Tcu51q7PGa]{Network of Contacts}, you can ask for a huge favor that puts the health of the informant at risk: traffic prohibited information, request for theft against minor nobles, make hot merchandise disappear or secure the services of a group of guards. Furthermore, by paying 1300 coins, there will be no limit to the request, as long as you does not clash with someone with a coinage value higher than your own.</span></p>",
